Package: duckhts
Title: DuckDB HTS File Reader Extension for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("DuckHTS", "Contributors",
    email = "dev@duckhts.invalid",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bundles the duckhts DuckDB extension for reading HTS file
    formats (VCF/BCF, SAM/BAM/CRAM, FASTA, FASTQ, GFF, GTF, tabix) from
    R via DuckDB. The extension and its htslib dependency are compiled from
    vendored sources during package installation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
OS_type: unix
SystemRequirements: GNU make, zlib, libbz2, liblzma, libcurl, openssl
Imports:
    DBI,
    utils
Suggests:
    duckdb,
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
